      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"أَيُّمَا اِمْرَأَةٍ خَرَجَتْ مِنْ بَيْتِهَا بِغَيْرِ إِذْنِ زَوْجِهَا فَلاَ نَفَقَةَ لَهَا حَتَّى تَرْجِعَ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4520 - Al-Sakuni narrated from Jafar ibn Muhammad, from his father (as), who said:\nThe Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace and blessings be upon him and his family) said:\n\"Any woman who leaves her house without her husband's permission has no right to maintenance until she returns.\""
        ]
      }
    },
